body:
**Zebra Katz** are a weird one, away from the now infamous, _Ima Read_, I’ve heard nothing by them that’s worth listening to more than once.

To be fair though, _Ima Read_ is MORE than worth listening to, a lot. Thankfully their new track _Pulla Stunt_, feat **Njena Reddd**, sees them back to their dark and at times monstrous ways; with dare I say it more than just one eye on the club. The dirt-ridden glitz now takes the form of a much more complex sonic arrangement, this could be more than just ‘the next buzz track’.

